('reply', 'Ill wipe the floor with you, %s, just like a ragged tabard.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, Ill drop you faster than Arthas dropped his humanity.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Even a gnome would laugh at your combat skills, %s.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Keep it up, %s, and you\'ll end up as vendor trash.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, Ill make you wish the Lich King raised you instead.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'I\'ll hunt you down to the ends of Azeroth, %s.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, you just signed your death warrant.', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
